hw01: NDC to RGB Shader

Tristan English
CSCI4239 Spring 2023

Takes points in NDC and converts to RGB colors

Scene setup, cube function, and CSCIx239.h library used from ex01

Approximate time spent: 4 hours

Key bindings
  z/Z        Move cube in z direction
  y/Y        Move cube in y direction
  x/X        Move cube in x direction
  m          Toggle shader
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
